extendedInfo.description: *Have a problem with the app starting and staying blank with Samsung Galaxy S3.Work around by turning on Developer options and checking the box for 'Disable Hardware overlays'.--------Slide a panel of railroad, Lead to the goal to train.[Instructions]Sliding a panel of railroad[Easy / Normal / Hard Level]Leads to the train by connecting railroad from start to finish.When there are no railroad in front of the train, it is a failed game.The distance to the goal, the resulting change in the number of red apples.[Endless Level]Get the coins on the board.Get the coin at a time, gradually increase the speed of the train.When there are no railroad in front of the train, it is a failed game.You can register your score online rankings.------------------------------[Resources]BGM is produced by PANICPUMPKIN.

reviews.title: It IS DIFFICULT!!!!!
reviews.comment: This is a fun, cute game that doesn\'t take much room and is so simple BUT for me anyway it\'s really difficult. Like someone else said I\'m surprised it has so few downloads
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Leave it to the Japanese to make puzzle sliding game this much fun, with trains.\tI mean that in the most respectable way. It should be getting way more downloads than it\'s gotten.

reviews.comment: May be a coincidence, but Market stopped working while I had this installed. Uninstalled and Market works again. Don\'t know why.
